          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "761 二年 置滑衛節度使，治滑州，領州六：滑、衛、相、魏、德、貝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "尋以德州隸淄沂節度而增領博州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "廢汴滑、河南二節度，以徐、泗、汴、宋、曹五州隸淮西節度，滑州隸滑衛節度。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "廢鄭陳節度，以鄭、陳、亳、潁四州隸淮西。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "淮南西道節度使增領陳、鄭、潁、亳、汴、曹、宋、徐、泗九州，徙治安州，號淮西十六州節度使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "尋以亳州隸滑衛節度，徐州隸兗鄆節度。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "置淄沂節度使，領淄、沂、滄、德、棣五州，治沂州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "平盧軍節度使侯希逸引兵保青州，授青密節度使，遂廢淄沂節度，並所管五州，號淄青平盧節度，增領齊州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "以齊 州隸青密，而兗鄆節度增領徐州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "766 大曆元年",
          "translations": [
